data.description: 3 bedroom 2 bath home  in LAKE FANTASIA! This home feels open and bright and has a fantastic view of the lake off your screened in porch. There is a storage area in the back and a large covered carport for your cars. The seller installed a new range, dishwasher, and microwave to help make this home move in ready! This great place is located in a desirable waterfront gated community with community center with fitness facility, sparkling pool, gazebo on a 50 acre lake with private boat ramp and basketball court, all located conveniently located between 41 and 301 where the owners own their land. This property is eligible under the Freddie Mac First Look Initiative through 03/17/2020
